<h1 id="referral-program">Referral Program</h1>
<h3 id="get-a-free-box-of-cinnamon-rolls-for-every-2-boxes-your-friends-buy">Get a free box of cinnamon rolls for every 2 boxes your friends buy!</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Refer your friends</li>
  <li>Receive a promo code in your email</li>
  <li>Redeem a free box of cinnamon rolls!</li>
</ol>

<p>The Referral Program ends July 31, 2022. Be sure to spread the word about @mishiesmunchies before then!</p>

<h3 id="details">Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Tell your friends about <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mishiesmunchies/">@mishiesmunchies</a>!</li>
  <li>Give them your email so that they can identify you as the referrer in the order form.</li>
  <li>After 2 boxes have been purchased with your email as the referrer, you will be sent a promo code.</li>
  <li>A promo code can be obtained when two friends each purchase a box <em>or</em> when one friend purchases two boxes in a single order.</li>
  <li>Promo codes are valid for a limited time only and expire on December 31, 2022. uture available order dates until December 31, 2022. Order dates are announced on this website and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mishiesmunchies/">@mishiesmunchies</a>.</li>
  <li>Promo codes are entered in the order form to redeem a free box of cinnamon rolls.</li>
  <li>
    <ul>
      <li>The referral program is a limited time offer that ends on July 31, 2022. All accumulated referrals will be lost once the program has ended.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li></li>
  <li>If want to know the status of your referrals, message <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mishiesmunchies/">@mishiesmunchies</a> on Instagram.</li>
</ul>

